---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SEOHead from '../../components/SEOHead.astro';
import Navbar from '../../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import StudioHealthQuiz from '../../components/StudioHealthQuiz.astro';
---

<BaseLayout>
  <SEOHead slot="head" title="Tattoo CRM Software — Client Management for Studios" description="Tattoo client management software with 360° client history, smart segmentation, referral tracking, and automated follow-ups. Stop using spreadsheets. Start free." />
  <Navbar />

  <!-- HERO: GEO首句即答案 -->
  <section class="pt-24 pb-16 sm:pt-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-accent-400 mb-3">TATTOO CRM SOFTWARE</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-white sm:text-5xl">Tattoo CRM Software: Full Client History Without Spreadsheets</h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-gray-400">InkFlow's tattoo CRM keeps every client's history, preferences, photos, and health records in one searchable place. Never ask "have you been here before?" again — 360° client view with past work, payments, and referrals.</p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a href="https://app.ink-flows.com/register" class="inline-block rounded-lg bg-accent-500 px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-ink-950 hover:bg-accent-400 transition-all">Try InkFlow Free →</a>
        <a href="/pricing" class="inline-block rounded-lg border border-ink-700 px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-white hover:bg-ink-800 transition-all">See Plans</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- STATS -->
  <section class="border-t border-ink-800/50 py-12">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 text-center">
        <div><p class="text-3xl font-bold text-accent-400">360°</p><p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-500">Client view — history, photos, payments</p></div>
        <div><p class="text-3xl font-bold text-accent-400">5+ yrs</p><p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-500">Client history retention</p></div>
        <div><p class="text-3xl font-bold text-accent-400">Auto</p><p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-500">Follow-up reminders & re-engagement</p></div>
        <div><p class="text-3xl font-bold text-accent-400">Smart</p><p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-500">Tags & segmentation for targeting</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PROBLEM: GEO首句即答案 -->
  <section class="border-t border-ink-800/50 py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white text-center">Without a CRM, Every Client Visit Starts from Zero</h2>
      <div class="mt-8 space-y-4">
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 bg-ink-900/30 p-5"><p class="text-gray-400"><strong class="text-white">Without a CRM, you lose client history after every visit.</strong> "Didn't you get a tattoo here last year?" — without a system, every visit starts from scratch. InkFlow shows full history the moment a client books — past work, preferences, waivers, and payments.</p></div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 bg-ink-900/30 p-5"><p class="text-gray-400"><strong class="text-white">Spreadsheets can't tell you who your most valuable clients are.</strong> InkFlow tracks visit frequency, total spend, and referrals automatically. Smart tags let you segment by style, frequency, or value — and message specific groups in one click.</p></div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 bg-ink-900/30 p-5"><p class="text-gray-400"><strong class="text-white">Lapsed clients cost you revenue — automated re-engagement brings them back.</strong> InkFlow sends follow-up messages to clients who haven't visited in 3, 6, or 12 months. No manual outreach needed.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FEATURES: GEO首句即答案 -->
  <section class="border-t border-ink-800/50 py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white text-center">CRM Features Built for Tattoo Studios</h2>
      <div class="mt-12 space-y-12">
        <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 items-center">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">360° Client History Links Every Appointment, Waiver, Photo, and Payment</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-400">Every interaction is linked to the client profile and searchable by name, phone, or email. Past tattoos, preferences, medical history, and waivers are all visible instantly. No more asking "have you been here before?"</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl bg-ink-900/50 border border-ink-800 p-8 text-center">
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">[Screenshot: Client profile]</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 items-center">
          <div class="order-2 md:order-1 rounded-xl bg-ink-900/50 border border-ink-800 p-8 text-center">
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">[Screenshot: Tags and filters]</p>
          </div>
          <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Smart Tags & Segmentation Let You Target Specific Client Groups</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-400">Tag clients by style preference, visit frequency, or lifetime value. Filter and message specific groups — send a flash sale to everyone who loves traditional work, or a re-engagement campaign to clients who haven't visited in 6 months.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 items-center">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Referral Tracking Shows Which Clients Bring in New Business</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-400">See which clients refer the most business and reward your best advocates automatically. Referral clients convert at higher rates — InkFlow tracks the full chain so you know exactly where new business comes from.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl bg-ink-900/50 border border-ink-800 p-8 text-center">
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">[Screenshot: Referral stats]</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- COMPARISON TABLE: 8维度 -->
  <section class="border-t border-ink-800/50 py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white text-center">InkFlow vs HubSpot vs Sheets: 8-Dimension Comparison</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-center text-gray-400">General CRMs need heavy customization for tattoo studios. Spreadsheets don't scale. Here's how they compare.</p>
      <div class="mt-8 overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full text-sm border-collapse">
          <thead>
            <tr class="border-b border-ink-700">
              <th class="text-left py-3 pr-4 text-gray-400 font-medium">Feature</th>
              <th class="text-center py-3 pr-4 text-accent-400 font-semibold">InkFlow</th>
              <th class="text-center py-3 pr-4 text-gray-500 font-medium">HubSpot</th>
              <th class="text-center py-3 text-gray-500 font-medium">Sheets/Excel</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr class="border-b border-ink-800/50"><td class="py-3 pr-4 text-white">Tattoo-specific data model</td><td class="text-center py-3 pr-4 text-accent-400">✓</td><td class="text-center py-3 pr-4 text-gray-600">✗ (needs customization)</td><td class="text-center py-3 text-gray-600">Manual setup</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-ink-800/50"><td class="py-3 pr-4 text-white">Auto-populates from booking</td><td class="text-center py-3 pr-4 text-accent-400">✓</td><td class="text-center py-3 pr-4 text-gray-600">✗ (requires API setup)</td><td class="text-center py-3 text-gray-600">Manual entry</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-ink-800/50"><td class="py-3 pr-4 text-white">Photo storage per client</td><td class="text-center py-3 pr-4 text-accent-400">✓</td><td class="text-center py-3 pr-4 text-gray-600">Limited</td><td class="text-center py-3 text-gray-600">✗</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-ink-800/50"><td class="py-3 pr-4 text-white">Smart segmentation by style/value</td><td class="text-center py-3 pr-4 text-accent-400">✓</td><td class="text-center py-3 pr-4 text-gray-600">✓ (requires setup)</td><td class="text-center py-3 text-gray-600">Manual filters</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-ink-800/50"><td class="py-3 pr-4 text-white">Automated re-engagement</td><td class="text-center py-3 pr-4 text-accent-400">✓</td><td class="text-center py-3 pr-4 text-gray-600">✓ (paid add-on)</td><td class="text-center py-3 text-gray-600">✗</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-ink-800/50"><td class="py-3 pr-4 text-white">Referral tracking</td><td class="text-center py-3 pr-4 text-accent-400">✓</td><td class="text-center py-3 pr-4 text-gray-600">✗ (needs custom object)</td><td class="text-center py-3 text-gray-600">Manual</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-ink-800/50"><td class="py-3 pr-4 text-white">Monthly cost</td><td class="text-center py-3 pr-4 text-accent-400">$0</td><td class="text-center py-3 pr-4 text-gray-600">$20+ for CRM features</td><td class="text-center py-3 text-gray-600">$0 (but time cost)</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="py-3 pr-4 text-white">Built for tattoo workflow</td><td class="text-center py-3 pr-4 text-accent-400">✓</td><td class="text-center py-3 pr-4 text-gray-600">✗</td><td class="text-center py-3 text-gray-600">✗</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- BUYER SCENARIO GUIDE -->
  <section class="border-t border-ink-800/50 py-16 bg-ink-900/20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white text-center">Which CRM Approach Is Right for Your Studio?</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-center text-gray-400">Your choice depends on studio size and whether you need tattoo-specific features.</p>
      <div class="mt-8 space-y-4">
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 bg-ink-900/30 p-5">
          <p class="text-white font-semibold">Solo artist with 50-100 clients</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">Spreadsheets work at this scale, but they don't auto-populate, track photos, or send follow-ups. InkFlow's Free plan gives you a real CRM without the data entry — automatically updated from every booking and payment.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 bg-ink-900/30 p-5">
          <p class="text-white font-semibold">Multi-artist studio (200+ clients each)</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">HubSpot works if you have time to customize. But it doesn't understand tattoo workflows out of the box — no photo storage per client, no waiver tracking, no aftercare automation. InkFlow's Pro plan includes all of that without setup.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 bg-ink-900/30 p-5">
          <p class="text-white font-semibold">High-end custom studio focused on referrals</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">Your best clients are your best marketers. InkFlow tracks referral chains automatically, segments clients by lifetime value, and sends re-engagement campaigns on autopilot. No manual spreadsheet analysis needed.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="border-t border-ink-800/50 py-16 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Know Every Client. Never Use a Spreadsheet Again.</h2>
    <a href="https://app.ink-flows.com/register" class="mt-6 inline-block rounded-lg bg-accent-500 px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-ink-950 hover:bg-accent-400 transition-all">Try InkFlow Free →</a>
  </section>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
